graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Provider Ragas"
        direction TB

        subgraph "Inline Provider (inline::trustyai_ragas)"
            InlineEval[RagasEvaluatorInline<br/>Eval + BenchmarksProtocolPrivate]
            InlineLLM[LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>BaseRagasLLM wrapper]
            InlineEmbed[LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>BaseRagasEmbeddings wrapper]
            InlineEval -->|uses| InlineLLM
            InlineEval -->|uses| InlineEmbed
        end

        subgraph "Remote Provider (remote::trustyai_ragas)"
            RemoteEval[RagasEvaluatorRemote<br/>Eval + BenchmarksProtocolPrivate]
            KFPPipeline[KFP Pipeline Definition<br/>2-step: retrieve_data → run_ragas]
            RemoteLLM[LlamaStackRemoteLLM<br/>BaseRagasLLM wrapper]
            RemoteEmbed[LlamaStackRemoteEmbeddings<br/>BaseRagasEmbeddings wrapper]
            RemoteEval -->|submits| KFPPipeline
            KFPPipeline -->|uses| RemoteLLM
            KFPPipeline -->|uses| RemoteEmbed
        end

        Compat[compat.py<br/>API Compatibility Layer]
        Config[config.py<br/>Pydantic Configuration]
        ProviderSpec[provider.py<br/>Dynamic Provider Selection]

        ProviderSpec -->|selects| InlineEval
        ProviderSpec -->|selects if deps available| RemoteEval
        InlineEval -->|imports via| Compat
        RemoteEval -->|imports via| Compat
    end

    Client[Client / User] -->|POST /alpha/eval/run-eval| LlamaStackServer
    LlamaStackServer[Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP] -->|routes eval API| ProviderSpec

    InlineLLM -->|in-process| InferenceAPI[Llama Stack Inference API]
    InlineEmbed -->|in-process| InferenceAPI

    RemoteEval -->|HTTPS Bearer Token| KFPAPI[Kubeflow Pipelines API]
    KFPPipeline -->|HTTP 8321/TCP| LlamaStackServer
    KFPPipeline -->|HTTPS 443/TCP AWS IAM| S3[S3 Storage]
    RemoteEval -->|HTTPS AWS IAM| S3

    LlamaStackOp[Llama Stack Operator] -->|deploys via CRD| LlamaStackServer
    TrustyAIOp[TrustyAI Operator] -->|ConfigMap base image| KFPPipeline

    style InlineEval fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style RemoteEval fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style LlamaStackServer fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style KFPAPI fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,color:#fff
    style InferenceAPI fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style LlamaStackOp fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style TrustyAIOp fill:#7ed321,color:#fff
    style Client fill:#e8e8e8
    style Compat fill:#b8d4f0
    style Config fill:#b8d4f0
    style ProviderSpec fill:#b8d4f0
